Manterror:

(Note: Jeniff, sorry, didn't see you fire at Manterror, though the Ark hasn't 
been seen to have windows, other than the cockpit's 'window', though I think  
it's safe to say the Autobots, the good race that they are/were, would have 
windows so they could admire the stars, or maybe not, I'll acknowledge the 
shot)

(Earlier, before Manterror entered the Ark)
::A fusion blast whistled through the air, Manterror jumped back, a burst of 
dirt hitting him in the face::
"Pth, pah." (Manterror spat, not seeing where the shot had coming from and 
entering the Ark)
